					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">To force Python 3 division behavior in Python 2, include the following <a href="https://docs.python.org/2/library/__future__.html" class="postlink">future statement</a> at the top of the program, after the shebang line (if present), other comments (if present), and the module docstring (if present), but before any code or other imports:<br /><div class="codetitle"><b>Code:</b></div><div class="codecontent">from __future__ import division</div></div>

