						<div class="postbody">Added support for note cuts to the converter (distro updated in OP). I hadn't used these very much in my compositions until now, now that I'm using them a lot it was pretty cumbersome to have an instrument that acts as a note cut with a silent volume envelope. This is much nicer.</div>

